      "passage_text": "Read the following instruction carefully and answer the questions given below.\nI. There is a rectangular wooden block of length 4 cm, height 3 cm and breadth 3 cm.\nII. The two opposite surface of 4 cm × 3 cm are painted yellow on the outside.\nIII. The other two opposite surface of 4 cm × 3 cm are painted red on the outside.\nIV. The remaining two surface of 3 cm × 3 cm are painted green on the outside.\nV. Now the block is cut in such a way that cubes of 1 cm × 1cm × 1 cm are created.",
      "has_figure": false,
      "topic_code": "puzzles"
    },
    {
      "passage_text": "Read the following information carefully and answer the questions given below.\nA cuboid of dimensions (6 cm × 4 cm × 1 cm) is painted black on both the surfaces of dimensions (4 cm × 1 cm), green on the surfaces of dimensions (6 cm × 4 cm) and red on the surfaces of dimensions (6 cm × 1 cm). Now, the block is divided into various smaller cubes of side 1 cm each. The smaller cubes so obtained are separated.",
      "has_figure": false,
      "topic_code": "puzzles"
    },
    {
